data.name: lblRules.Text
data.value: Your task is to slay the monster that has been terrorizing across the land for decades. There is a large bounty on this monsters head and your name will have a reputation that will spread across the continent.

data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
Hit Percentage: Each ability has a percent chance of being sucessfull. For example if the hit chance is 60% then that move will only work 60% of the time that you use it.
Critical Hits: Each ability has a 10% chance of being a critical hit, doubling the value the ability gives in ethier damage or health.
